query:
INSERT INTO project_group
                (
                    id,
                    name,
                    owner,
                    description,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
                )
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
                ON CONFLICT (id)
                DO UPDATE SET
                    name        = EXCLUDED.name,
                    owner       = EXCLUDED.owner,
                    updated_at  = EXCLUDED.updated_at
